quran[8{c,v,t}:
28,6,aur zameen mein un ko Iqtidaar bakhsheen aur un se firaon o Haman aur un ke lashkaron ko wohi kuch dikhla den jis ka inhen dar tha
28,7,"hum ne moose ki maa ko ishara kya ke"" iss ko doodh pila, phir jab tujhe uss ki jaan ka khatrah ho to usay darya mein daal day aur kuch khauf aur gham nah kar, hum usay tairay hi paas wapas le ayen ge aur is ko payghambaroon mein shaamil karen ge """
28,8,"aa خرکار firaon ke ghar walon ne usay ( darya se ) nikaal liya taakay woh un ka dushman aur un ke liye Sabab ranj banay, waqai firaon aur Haman aur is ke lashkar ( apni tadbeer mein ) barray ghalat car thay"
28,9,"firaon ki biwi ne ( is se ) kaha"" yeh mere aur tairay liye aankhon ki thandak hai, usay qatal nah karo, kya ajab ke yeh hamaray liye mufeed saabit ho, ya hum usay beta hi bana len"" aur woh ( injaam se ) be khabar thay"
28,10,udhar moose ki maa ka dil ura ja raha tha woh is raaz ko faash kar bithti agar hum is ki dhaaras nah bandha dete taakay woh ( hamaray waday par ) imaan laane walon mein se ho
28,11,uss ne bachay ki behan se kaha is ke peechay peechay ja chunancha woh allag se is ko is terhan dekhatii rahi ke ( dushmanon ko ) is ka pata nah chala
28,12,"aur hum ne bachay par pehlay hi dُodh pilanay valyon ki chhatiyan haraam kar rakhi theen ( yeh haalat dekh kar ) uss larki ne unn se kaha"" mein tumhe aisay ghar ka pata batau jis ke log is ki parwarish ka zmmh len aur kher khawahi ke sath usay rakhen? """
28,13,"is terhan hum moose ko is ki maa ke paas palta laaye taakay is ki ankhen thandhi hon aur woh ghamgeen nah ho aur jaan le ke Allah ka wada sacha tha, magar aksar log is baat ko nahi jantay"
